{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-4", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "赤雪之兆", "storyInfo": "小队被隔开。梓兰和空爆战胜拦路的野兽，另一边，宝巫迦也击败了“异兽”，然而，倒下的“异兽”竟再次站了起来......", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g5_snowymountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“兔团子”还真不赖，吃完感觉身上暖洋洋的，充满了力量！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是当然的喵！“兔团子”不仅能填饱肚子，不同的口味还能给猎人带来各种神奇的效果喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "总觉得......有种不好的预感。这里的空气，让人很不舒服。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“诅咒”的气息，而且越来越浓郁了。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？你们有没有觉得......好像没那么冷了？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是错觉。你看脚下！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "众人低头看去，只见脚下厚厚的积雪正在以肉眼可见的速度融化，露出其下黑色的火山岩。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周围的空气迅速变得灼热、干燥，甚至开始弥漫起一股硫磺的味道。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是怎么回事喵？！雪山怎么变成火山了喵？！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“异兽”的“诅咒”......它在凭借自己的力量，将这里的环境改造成更适合它自己的战场！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "远处的雪峰上，一道火光冲天而起，紧接着，滚烫的岩浆从山顶流淌而下，将白色的雪地染成一片触目惊心的赤红。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊啊！真的喷发了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾能感觉到，雪山之中有一股正在酝酿的巨大能量......一定是熔火蜗，它想要用“诅咒”的力量将整座雪山改造成火山！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不对......“诅咒”的能量不止一处......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有两个不同的能量点，雪山之中的那个最为巨大！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你说什么？！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必须去阻止它！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "loop": "false", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，他们脚下的地面裂开一道巨大的缝隙，灼热的岩浆从地缝中喷涌而出，瞬间隔断了队伍。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰小姐！空爆小姐！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐！宝巫迦她——", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啧，居然来这一手......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "翔虫——可恶，这些岩浆太碍事了，翔虫也飞不过去！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......只能如此了。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "两位，吾去解决雪山之中的那个能量点，你们只要想办法自保就好！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宝巫迦，等等！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啧，这孩子怎么这么喜欢一个人把事情揽下来！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2104_1#1$2", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，正好喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就让我们看看你们的修行成果吧喵。义经，我们退后喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "义经发出一声低沉的吼声，像是在说“别让我们失望”。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？你们不上吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是属于你们的第一次考验，是检验你们是否有资格被称为猎人的考试喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$5"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空爆，准备好了吗？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，当然！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我用曲射限制它的走位，你找机会给它的腿来一下！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attribute