ntent": "梓兰正蹲在地上，仔细地处理着空爆身上的伤口，她的眉头紧锁。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿。梓兰姐，我刚才可帅了！熔火蜗虽然也很厉害，但是——", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰手上的动作加重了一分。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疼疼疼，梓兰姐，轻点。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我就知道，你拿上这把武器，就多半会变成这样子。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是——嘶，好疼！但是，梓兰姐，你不觉得很有趣吗？狩猎真是太好玩了。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你这一身伤，我是看不出有什么好玩的。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是那种......拼尽全力，用智慧和勇气战胜比自己强大无数倍的对手的感觉！", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可不想懂。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只看到你为了所谓的“帅气”，连我的命令都不听了。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我那不是不听命令啦！我......", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "义经说得没错。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？义经说什么了来着？", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他说我一直在下意识地回避近身战斗。他说对了。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你呢，空爆？政宗也说你太乱来了。你难道就不觉得自己刚才是在用自己的命去赌吗？", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（政宗也说我乱来......但是，不那么做的话，就感觉......就感觉抓不住那一瞬间的机会......）", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那种心脏快要跳出来的感觉，那种把一切都赌在那一瞬间的感觉......）", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真搞不懂，对你来说，狩猎到底是什么。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空爆闻言歪了歪头，她想要和平常一样找点俏皮话回答，但话到了嘴边，不知道为什么，忽然说不出口了。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默在两人之间盘桓，只有一边的烤肉架发出的滋滋声证明着时间的流逝。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g5_snowymountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2104_1#1$2", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing5", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原来如此，这一代的“异兽”，居然是一只如此巨大的熔火蜗。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先奴役了一只普通的熔火蜗，凭借“诅咒”想要将整座雪山改造成火山，改造成更适合你们生存的地方。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然后，将吾等分散，想要各个击破。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，你犯了两个错误......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一，你没有意识到，梓兰小姐和空爆小姐很强。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，你自己也应该感觉到了，“诅咒”的力度已经减弱了许多，那个比你弱小的“诅咒”源已经消失了。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她们已经消灭了你的手下吧。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而第二个错误——就是成为吾的对手。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "受死吧。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_heavy", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bone_rub", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2104_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（虚弱的吼叫）", "name": "“异兽”熔火蜗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2104_1#1$2"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g5_snowymountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "发生了什么？！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宝巫迦感到，在她的脚下，在更深更远的地下，有什么东西正在吸引着她。"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这股吸力过于强大，以至于她感到自己的灵魂正被抽离出身体。"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的痛苦填满了她，让她连呼吸都有些困难。"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同时，已经倒在地上的“异兽”熔火蜗尸体忽然爆发出冲天的黑气，伴随着黑气的逐渐旺盛，它居然缓缓地从地上爬了起来。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2104_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"c